|---|---|
| `helmet()` | Sets CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, etc. |
| `disable('x-powered-by')` | Removes Express version disclosure |
| `express.json({ limit })` | Prevents large-payload DoS |
| `express-rate-limit` | Mitigates brute-force & scraping |
| `express-validator` | Whitelists/sanitizes inputs; rejects bad types |
| Generic 400/500 messages | Avoids leaking internal details or reflecting attacker input |
| Central error handler | Prevents stack-trace disclosure |
| Route-level `try/catch → next(err)` | Ensures async errors reach the handler |
| Removed `email` from `/users` | Don't expose PII without authN/authZ |
| Graceful shutdown | Prevents dropped in-flight requests and zombie processes |
| `PORT` from env | Supports secure deployment config |

